---
title: Smart Veggie-Loaded Shrimp Green Curry with Lime-Scented Couscous
description: Feeling like takeout without all the waiting? This green curry with salmon is speedy and packed with veggies. Served with fluffy couscous, scented with lime, this is craveable!

